<span class='tline' id='l178' data-llen='2765:2789'>大宗伯云以𤣥璜禮北方牲幣皆如璜色後鄭云以立</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l179' data-llen='2789:2813'>冬祭黒精之帝而顓頊𤣥冥食焉半璧曰璜象冬閉藏</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l180' data-llen='2813:2836'>地上無物唯天半見賈釋云列宿為天文草木為地文</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l181' data-llen='2836:2854'>冬草木零落惟列宿在天故云唯天半見</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l182' data-llen='2854:2881'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0078', 'WYG', '011-15a' );" name="011-15a" class="pb">[011-15a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
